Description:
    Create Vue files from model corresponding to the Rails views

Example:
    rails generate vue SomeModel
    
    This will create:
        create  app/javascript/views/some_models/index.vue
        create  app/javascript/views/some_models/edit.vue
        create  app/javascript/views/some_models/new.vue
        create  app/javascript/views/some_models/_form.vue
        create  app/javascript/packs/vuex/modules/some_models/some_models.js

        modify app/javascript/packs/router/index.js
        modify app/javascript/packs/lib/slideMenuItems_dev.js